{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhueh4fo7yo0","created":1776324479514,"text":"系统架构设计"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhueiaqjis80","created":1776324571596,"text":"架构4+1（罗凯进五常）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhueif38mj40","created":1776324581071,"text":"逻辑视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhueimtnvrc0","created":1776324597907,"text":"开发视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhueip4a5k00","created":1776324602902,"text":"进程视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhueirhzv0w0","created":1776324608085,"text":"物理视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhueiufba8w0","created":1776324614454,"text":"+1 场景"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuejpnhnk80","created":1776324682428,"text":"RUP和UML的4+1（落实进步用）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuejvl9vyg0","created":1776324695355,"text":"逻辑视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuejxccaj40","created":1776324699168,"text":"实现视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuek14sha00","created":1776324707419,"text":"进程视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuek6fuxo00","created":1776324718972,"text":"部署视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuek81xcwg0","created":1776324722483,"text":"+1 用例"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuekdbhctk0","created":1776324733945,"text":"ABSD中4+1（落实进配）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuekkizvy80","created":1776324749636,"text":"逻辑视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhueknl021s0","created":1776324756288,"text":"实现视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuekoxf5so0","created":1776324759216,"text":"进程视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuekqf5vao0","created":1776324762465,"text":"配置视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuekrhce800","created":1776324764774,"text":"+1 用例"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuemfy1oug0","created":1776324896391,"text":" ABSD"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuenrn7v1c0","created":1776325000222,"text":"基于体系结构的软件设计"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuer5dc0ao0","created":1776325265191,"text":"由构成体系结构的商业、质量和功能需求的组合驱动"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhueruf4d3k0","created":1776325319719,"text":"3个基础"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuerwrmey80","created":1776325324829,"text":"功能分解"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhues1ijlrs0","created":1776325335163,"text":"通过选择体系结构风格来实现质量和商业需求"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhues9yypts0","created":1776325353571,"text":"使用软件模版"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuevt5kjz40","created":1776325630421,"text":"基于体系结构的开发"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuew5032vc0","created":1776325656211,"text":"子过程（许设温敷试验）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuewjlv0co0","created":1776325688003,"text":"需求"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuex592fdk0","created":1776325735118,"text":"系统质量目标"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuex8d462g0","created":1776325741894,"text":"商业目标"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuexb590w00","created":1776325747948,"text":"开发人员商业目标"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuewl9mlio0","created":1776325691617,"text":"设计"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuewmidp5s0","created":1776325694323,"text":"文档化"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuey75rj6g0","created":1776325817636,"text":"输出"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuey82fim00","created":1776325819612,"text":"体系结构规格说明书"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhueyfm5bd40","created":1776325836041,"text":"测试质量设计说明书"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuewnmpg0g0","created":1776325696761,"text":"复审"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuewr0m3so0","created":1776325704132,"text":"实现"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuexvlaa6o0","created":1776325792454,"text":"演化"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuezj3v6iw0","created":1776325922007,"text":"需求变化归类"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuezoiysrs0","created":1776325933804,"text":"制定演化计划"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf03g6zt40","created":1776325966288,"text":"修改/增加/扇出构件"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf07426qo0","created":1776325974262,"text":"更新构件的相互作用"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf0by6ceg0","created":1776325984790,"text":"构件组装与测试"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf0f0sth40","created":1776325991479,"text":"技术评审"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuhs5b1jrs0","created":1776333806747,"text":"定义"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuhs6fwyig0","created":1776333809218,"text":"ABSD 方法是一个自顶向下，递归细化的方法，软件系\n统的体系结构通过该方法得到细化，直到能产生软件构\n件和类。在最顶层，系统被分解为若干概念子系统和一\n个或若干个软件模板。在第 2 层，概念子系统又被分解\n成概念构件和一个或若干个附加软件模板。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-151,"y":4}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf92m8rco0","created":1776326669755,"text":"软件架构风格"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuf96cbrqg0","created":1776326677862,"text":"概念"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuf97jof1c0","created":1776326680484,"text":"定义一个词汇表和一组约束，词汇表包含构件和连接\n件。反应了众多系统所共有的结构和语义特性，并指导\n如何将各个模块和子系统有效地组成一个完整的系统。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-46,"y":-8}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhufbg23h1k0","created":1776326855740,"text":"分类"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufrtfhewg0","created":1776328138674,"text":"数据流风格","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufbgxr0ig0","created":1776326857654,"text":"批处理风格"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufcfnq2h40","created":1776326933235,"text":"每个步骤是一个单独的程序，每一步必须在前一步结束\n后才能开始，并且数据必须是完成的，以整体的方式传\n递。它的基本构件是独立的应用程序，连接件是某种类\n型的媒介。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhufbz9oq0g0","created":1776326897558,"text":"管道/过滤器风格"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufqmpjmns0","created":1776328045681,"text":"一个步骤的输出是另一个步骤的输入，可以并行处理；\n基本构件是过滤器，连接件是数据流传输管道。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhufshmr5n40","created":1776328191356,"text":"调用/返回风格"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufskvk7vc0","created":1776328198419,"text":"主/子程序风格"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhufsqtpp280","created":1776328211368,"text":"面向对象风格"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhufsu4y97s0","created":1776328218578,"text":"层次型风格"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuft7kp80w0","created":1776328247829,"text":"客户端/服务器风格"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug0ypb5vc0","created":1776328855430,"text":"以数据为中心"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug11q5wdk0","created":1776328862012,"text":"仓库风格"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug1etnfw80","created":1776328890521,"text":"仓库是存储和维护数据的中心场所。例如现代IDE、企业级数据管理系统"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug16ag2g80","created":1776328871945,"text":"黑板风格"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug2hyxmyw0","created":1776328975735,"text":"类虚拟机"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug2o4yrkw0","created":1776328989160,"text":"解释器风格"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug2t4tw1c0","created":1776329000036,"text":"规则系统风格"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug2z8zcjs0","created":1776329013347,"text":"独立构件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug327n5co0","created":1776329019797,"text":"进程通信风格"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug36oxqbc0","created":1776329029550,"text":"事件系统风格"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug3kdwzps0","created":1776329059358,"text":"c2风格"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug3vnqriw0","created":1776329083897,"text":"构件和连接件都有顶部和底部"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug40p8rxc0","created":1776329094872,"text":"构件之前不允许直接连接"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug46g63ow0","created":1776329107384,"text":"连接件可以连接任意数量的构件和其它连接件"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug4gdeyxk0","created":1776329128985,"text":"当两个连接件直接相连时，必须一个底部连接到另一个的顶部"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug4vnz9fc0","created":1776329162275,"text":"闭环控制风格"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug5451y880","created":1776329180722,"text":"比如空调控温度，定速巡航"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug5ojrzts0","created":1776329225148,"text":"软件架构复用"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuhvk1mhdk0","created":1776334073921,"text":"是指在多个软件系统或项目中重复使用已有的架构设\n计、组件、模式、技术或构件，以提高开发效率、降低\n成本、提高软件质量和可维护性；主要分为机会复用和\n系统复用；","layout_left_offset":{"x":-51,"y":4}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv3zm9rhzc0","created":1776396456642,"text":"软件产品线"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv3zreql5c0","created":1776396467827,"text":"核心资产库：设计方案及其文档、用户手册、项目管\n理的历史记录、软件测试计划和测试用例"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv41cfe24g0","created":1776396591943,"text":"基本过程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv41ejui8w0","created":1776396596566,"text":"构造/获取可复用的资产"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv41iqs1i80","created":1776396605692,"text":"管理可复用资产"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv41mtdp3k0","created":1776396614556,"text":"使用可复用资产"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv423ykimg0","created":1776396651875,"text":"特定领域软件体系结构 - DSSA"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv434kfd5k0","created":1776396731561,"text":"分类"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv435isnvk0","created":1776396733639,"text":"垂直域，只能应用于成熟、稳定的领域"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv438cz0kw0","created":1776396739818,"text":"水平域"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv43qy8jm80","created":1776396780285,"text":"基本活动"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv43tm7vyo0","created":1776396786089,"text":"领域分析"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv43uw24zc0","created":1776396788861,"text":"领域设计"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv43w35myg0","created":1776396791467,"text":"领域实现"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv43zucx7k0","created":1776396799642,"text":"参与人员"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv4413ag7k0","created":1776396802359,"text":"领域专家"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv445nkoug0","created":1776396812292,"text":"领域分析人员"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv447n5gps0","created":1776396816620,"text":"领域设计人员"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv449z8otk0","created":1776396821705,"text":"领域实现人员"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv44ier9vs0","created":1776396840057,"text":"建立过程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv44jpkqqw0","created":1776396842888,"text":"定义领域范围"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv44lhpd5s0","created":1776396846766,"text":"定义领域特性元素"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv44pcarqg0","created":1776396855146,"text":"定义领域特定的设计和实现需求约束"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv44xxws1s0","created":1776396873867,"text":"定义领域模型和体系结构"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv45238no00","created":1776396882897,"text":"产生、搜集可重用的产品单元"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv7fqjoig80","created":1776406183105,"text":"架构评估"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv7h9ah7qw0","created":1776406302272,"text":"软件系统质量属性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv8cp7s5pk0","created":1776408766226,"text":"开发期质量属性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8cru43vk0","created":1776408771930,"text":"运行期质量属性"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv7hdmhdgg0","created":1776406311705,"text":"软件架构质量属性\n强调如何通过架构设计实现和优化质量属性","layout_left_offset":{"x":-20,"y":65}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv7igiq6qg0","created":1776406396372,"text":"性能"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv7j65kkuw0","created":1776406452173,"text":"系统的响应能力，TPS、QPS或响应时间"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv7iim50sg0","created":1776406400932,"text":"可靠性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv7k1q17a80","created":1776406520890,"text":"在意外错误使用情况下维持功能特性的基本能力，通过\n平均失效时间来衡量","layout_left_offset":{"x":-57,"y":0}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv7ik04yi00","created":1776406403955,"text":"可用性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv7kxxyljc0","created":1776406591027,"text":"系统正常运行的时间比例"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv7ioepoz40","created":1776406413544,"text":"安全性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv87eg9ne80","created":1776408350974,"text":"向合法用户提供服务的同时阻止非授权访问"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv7iro9ypk0","created":1776406420652,"text":"可修改性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv87zxyaao0","created":1776408397756,"text":"快速、高性价比地变更系统的能力，包括可维护性、可\n扩展性、易重构","layout_left_offset":{"x":-3,"y":-6}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv7itbqpr40","created":1776406424248,"text":"互操作性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv7ivex1xs0","created":1776406428793,"text":"可移植性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv89vd94e00","created":1776408544525,"text":"适应不同运行环境的能力"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv7iyzrknc0","created":1776406436584,"text":"可测试性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv89og77pc0","created":1776408529466,"text":"易用性"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8doks7o80","created":1776408843200,"text":"质量属性场景","layout_left_offset":{"x":2,"y":49}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv8dyj3zgg0","created":1776408864866,"text":"目的：精确描述软件系统的质量属性","layout_left_offset":{"x":-71,"y":11}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8ehlk9ts0","created":1776408906373,"text":"概念：质量属性场景是对利益相关者与系统交互的简短\n陈述，描述一个具体的质量属性需求","layout_left_offset":{"x":-51,"y":14}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8ff158000","created":1776408979149,"text":"组成部分"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv8fghufmo0","created":1776408982336,"text":"刺激源"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv8g4w5ppc0","created":1776409035444,"text":"生成刺激的实体"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8fj282zs0","created":1776408987922,"text":"刺激"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv8g9blgf40","created":1776409045085,"text":"到达系统时需考虑的条件"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8fkc2nfc0","created":1776408990694,"text":"环境"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv8ghvx0oo0","created":1776409063728,"text":"刺激发生的条件"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8fl5z9fc0","created":1776408992502,"text":"制品"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv8gldbzhk0","created":1776409071311,"text":"被激励的对象"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8fmabrmo0","created":1776408994942,"text":"响应"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv8gowt3vk0","created":1776409079019,"text":"激励到达后采取的行动"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8fn5vcco0","created":1776408996849,"text":"响应度量"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8fr8cy2o0","created":1776409005707,"text":"质量属性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv8fsriqw00","created":1776409009042,"text":"可用性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8fu8o8sw0","created":1776409012256,"text":"可修改性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8fw1v68g0","created":1776409016198,"text":"性能"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8fz47hmg0","created":1776409022870,"text":"可测试性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8g0dqag00","created":1776409025623,"text":"易用性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv8g1qa5kg0","created":1776409028559,"text":"安全性"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}